data.description: Wonderfully updated home in Josephine! Cul-de-sac location with no HOA or MUD tax! This 3 bedroom 2 bath home features a galley style kitchen. The white cabinetry with butcher block counters and stainless appliances give it a modern touch. The primary bedroom with ensuite bath and walk-in closet give the future owner their own private space. Updates include: Solar screens, 8 ft privacy fence, exterior paint, new sinks, faucets, fixtures, water heater, front and back doors, luxury vinyl flooring and freshly painted exterior. Outside, a large backyard is perfect for outdoor activities and potential family gatherings, a fully insulated building with electricity and water, and attached 20x20 carport or covered shed. Energy-efficient features: R19 blown insulation, 26 gauge R panel galvalume class 4 metal roof, save on electric and insurance! A great price point for a first time buyer! Seller will consider covering buyer's closing costs or rate buy down!
